    },
    {
      "end": 57.720001220703125,
      "text": "Now they like, ooh, ooh, ooh, what he do? I'm like, poop, poop, poop, hop out on you. Don't care if you like that, I love it. I'm just here with the gunman above it.",
      "start": 47.52000045776367
    },
    {
      "end": 67,
      "text": "Taking over the body with my poses. Taking out everybody like a god with the ocean and emotion. Feeling that one spectacular emotion of hate. Let the gun go, debate.",
      "start": 57.720001220703125
    },
    {
      "end": 78.72000122070312,
      "text": "What you say? What does God, God without me, who am I? If I am not he, I'm demonized. My confidence got me paralyzed. I refuse to believe in a dead man till I die.",
      "start": 67.66000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 88.37999725341797,
      "text": "What you say? What does God, God without me, who am I? If I am not he, I'm demonized. My confidence got me paralyzed. I refuse to believe in a dead man till I die.",
      "start": 78.72000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 97.69999694824219,
      "text": "I could get you on a round, I was into leaving. Coating the unknown with nothing to believe in. Bruised up and beat down, then turn to bleeding. I see death is in the air, I can feel it in my breathing.",
      "start": 88.4000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 105.19999694824219,
      "text": "Plus my odds are getting lower, gotta guess the reason. How am I awake? It feel like I am dreaming. A rose by any name is just a flower out of season.",
      "start": 97.69999694824219
    },
    {
      "end": 112.44000244140625,
      "text": "Depends how it rise from die or the cement. Apparently my future's only relevant in past tense. That's the case and clearly not in the present.",
      "start": 105.5199966430664
    },
    {
      "end": 121.68000030517578,
      "text": "It's common sense, maybe you should take a second and figure out what I've hidden in my message. Instead of being blinded by your own objections, protection is intended for subjection.",
      "start": 112.9000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 126.5199966430664,
      "text": "Only God can judge me, nigga, what's with all the questions? Absolution itself is motive for depression.",
      "start": 121.68000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 147,
      "text": "What is God, what is God without me, who am I? If I am not he, I'm demonized. My confidence got me paralyzed. I refuse to believe in a dead man till I die.",
      "start": 127.30000305175781
    },
    {
      "end": 157.27999877929688,
      "text": "Till I die, I'll be singing your praise. No inner level here, let's all get the raise you had to face.",
      "start": 147
    },
    {
      "end": 163.05999755859375,
      "text": "Why not? Fake Mr. Rogers said fuck you, bitch.",
      "start": 158.5
    }
